===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

The Hewlett-Packard Company thanks Joshua Small of Technion for reporting
CVE-2013-6211 to security-alert@...com

RESOLUTION

HP has made the following updates available for this issue

